      <p class="section-subtitle">Please download, complete and return the relevant agreement form before your event. This helps us ensure a smooth booking process.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="downloads-grid stagger">
      <div class="download-card">
        <div class="download-icon">
          <i class="fas fa-music"></i>
        </div>
        <div class="download-content">
          <h3>Mobile DJ Hire Agreement</h3>
          <p>Required for all DJ hire bookings. Includes terms of service, equipment details, payment terms and event requirements.</p>
          <ul class="download-features">
            <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Equipment list included</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Payment terms</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Cancellation policy</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="/media/downloads/D Batchelor Enterprises mobile DJ  HIRE AGREEMENT.docx" download class="btn btn-primary">
            <i class="fas fa-download"></i> Download DJ Agreement
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="download-card">
        <div class="download-icon">
          <i class="fas fa-glass-cheers"></i>
        </div>
        <div class="download-content">
          <h3>Party Equipment Hire Agreement</h3>
          <p>Required for party equipment hire bookings. Includes equipment inventory, hire conditions, damage policy and return requirements.</p>
          <ul class="download-features">
            <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Full equipment inventory</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Hire conditions</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Damage policy</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="/media/downloads/D Batchelor Enterprises PARTY HIRE AGREEMENT.docx" download class="btn btn-primary">
            <i class="fas fa-download"></i> Download Party Hire Agreement
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Important Notes -->
    <div class="download-notes reveal mt-4">
      <div class="notes-card">
        <h3><i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i> Important Information</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Please complete and sign the relevant agreement form and return it to us before your event.</li>
          <li>A 50% deposit is required to confirm your booking.</li>
          <li>For DJ hire, the remaining balance is due 7 days before your event.</li>
          <li>For party hire, the full payment is required at time of collection.</li>
          <li>If you have any questions, please <a href="/contact">contact us</a>.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Contact CTA -->
